    <!-- /.content-tab-panel -->
    <div id="source-tab" class="content-tab-panel">
<table><tr><td>Easty A, Coakley N, Cheng R, Cividino M, Savage P, Tozer R, White R, Safe Handling of Cytotoxics Expert Panel. Safe handling of cytotoxics. Toronto (ON): Cancer Care Ontario (CCO); 2013 Dec 16. 75 p.&nbsp;(Evidence-based series; no. 16-3).&nbsp; [61 references]</td></tr></table>                    <p><a href="/web/20180712210914/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=47792&amp;contentType=fulltextlink&amp;redirect=https%253a%252f%252fwww.cancercare.on.ca%252fcommon%252fpages%252fUserFile.aspx%253ffileId%253d293471">View the original guideline documentation</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712210914im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p>
    </div>
    <!-- /.content-tab-panel -->
    <div id="status-tab" class="content-tab-panel">
            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: Green E, Johnston M, Macartney G, Milliken D, Poirier S, Reynolds P, et al. Safe handling of parenteral cytotoxics. Toronto (ON): Cancer Care Ontario; 2007 Apr 13.</p>
<p>The EVIDENCE-BASED SERIES report, initially the full original Guideline, over time will expand to contain new information emerging from their reviewing and updating activities.</p>
<p>Please visit the <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180712210914/https://www.cancercare.on.ca/common/pages/UserFile.aspx?fileId=293471" title="Cancer Care Ontario Web site">Cancer Care Ontario Web site</a> for details on any new evidence that has emerged and implications to the guidelines.</p></div></p>
    </div>
    <!-- /.content-tab-panel -->
    <div id="classification-tab" class="content-tab-panel">


        
