<p>The working group members declared no conflicts of interest except for AE, who is president and owns a medical consulting company. This company is not engaged in any work related to cytotoxic handling.</p>
<p>The guideline development group members and targeted peer reviewers declared no conflicts of interest except for ER, who was a committee member on a Canadian Standards Association (CSA) standard used in this guideline.</p>
